20we%20will%20%E2%80%94%20frankly%2C%20we%20will%20challenge%20that%20history.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20three%20executives%20have%20their%20own%20bona%20fides.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fted-pick-morgan-stanley-frontrunner-james-gorman-successor-2023-8%5C%22%3ETed%20Pick%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20hard-charging%20investment%20bank%20boss%2C%20is%20credited%20with%20transforming%20Morgan%20Stanley's%20key%20equities%20and%20fixed-income%20businesses.%20His%20main%20competition%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmorgan-stanley-james-gorman-ceo-successors-pick-saperstein-simkowitz-2023-5%5C%22%3EAndy%20Saperstein%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20leads%20the%20bank's%20%244.8%20trillion%20wealth%20manager%2C%20which%20has%20buoyed%20the%20firm's%20revenue%20as%20dealmaking%20has%20ground%20to%20a%20halt.%20The%20dark%20horse%20Dan%20Simkowitz%20runs%20asset%20management%2C%20which%20is%20the%20bank's%20smallest%20business%20line%20but%20its%20assets%20have%20nearly%20quadrupled%20to%20%241.4%20trillion%20under%20his%20eight-year%20tenure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20Morgan%20Stanley%20at%20the%20top%20of%20its%20game%2C%20breaking%20up%20this%20well-oiled%20team%20could%20be%20disastrous.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20company%20can%20still%20be%20as%20good%20as%20it%20is%20now%20under%20the%20leadership%20of%20whoever%20gets%20it.%20The%20goal%20should%20be%20to%20be%20an%20even%20better%20version%20of%20what%20they%20are%20now%2C%20which%20is%20pretty%20damn%20good%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20analyst%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20the%20one%20thing%20you%20don't%20want%20to%20do%20is%20put%20that%20at%20risk.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInsider%20spoke%20to%20analysts%20and%20nine%20former%20colleagues%20of%20the%20trio.%20Here%20is%20what%20you%20need%20to%20know%20about%20the%20three%20candidates%20to%20run%20the%20Wall%20Street%20megabank.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ETed%20Pick%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%2054-year-old%20trader%20has%20made%20his%20name%20as%20Morgan%20Stanley's%20problem%20solver%20by%20turning%20around%20the%20bank's%20equities%20and%20fixed-income%20businesses.%20Pick%2C%20who%20has%20spent%20his%20entire%20career%20at%20Morgan%20Stanley%2C%20quickly%20earned%20a%20reputation%20as%20a%20hard-working%20%26quot%3Bdeal%20junkie.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe's%20the%20guy%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20a%20really%20tough%20deal%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20former%20superior%20said.%20%26quot%3BTed%20is%20working%20the%20phones%2C%20he's%20talking%2C%20he's%20in%20communication%20with%20the%20investors%20who%20say%20no%2C%20and%20he%20understands%20it.%20He's%20just%20really%20good%20at%20closing%20and%20intense%20about%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPick%2C%20whose%20old%20habit%20of%20cursing%20has%20made%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.efinancialcareers.com%2Fnews%2Ffinance%2Fted-pick-morgan-stanley%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eheadlines%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20is%20also%20known%20for%20not%20pulling%20punches%2C%20even%20with%20clients.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20easy%20to%20fall%20in%20love%20with%20your%20own%20line%20of%20patter%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Blackstone's%20Tony%20James%2C%20who%20chose%20Pick%20to%20advise%20on%20the%20private%20equity%20giant's%20initial%20public%20offering.%20%26quot%3BHe'd%20call%20you%20out%20on%20that%20in%20a%20heartbeat%20and%20say%2C%20'That's%20not%20gonna%20fly.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20biggest%20obstacle%20standing%20in%20Pick's%20way%20is%20a%20federal%20probe%20into%20Morgan%20Stanley's%20block-trading%20business%2C%20which%20falls%20under%20his%20purview.%20That%20same%20unit%20lost%20nearly%20a%20billion%20dollars%20in%20the%202021%20implosion%20of%20investment%20firm%20Archegos%20Capital%20Management.%20(Morgan%20Stanley%20has%20stated%20it%20is%20cooperating%20with%20regulators).%20There%20are%20no%20indications%20that%20Pick%20or%20the%20bank%20have%20been%20implicated%20in