mkowitz%20did%20work%20on%20record%20deals%20during%20his%20time%20in%20the%20investment%20bank%2C%20including%20the%20IPO%20of%20oil%20refiner%20Conoco%20and%20Verizon's%20%2449%20billion%20bond%20offering.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20has%20experience%20in%20Washington%2C%20D.C.%2C%20that%20could%20come%20in%20handy.%20Wall%20Street%20is%20girding%20itself%20for%20the%20government%20to%20impose%20higher%20capital%20requirements%20as%20part%20of%20what%20would%20be%20the%20most%20significant%20banking%20overhaul%20since%20the%20Dodd-Frank%20Act.%20Starting%20in%202008%2C%20Simkowitz%20spent%20four%20years%20advising%20the%20Federal%20Reserve%20and%20Treasury%20on%20the%20restructuring%20of%20Fannie%20Mae%20and%20Freddie%20Mac%20as%20well%20as%20the%20public%20offerings%20of%20General%20Motors%2C%20AIG%2C%20and%20Citigroup.%20Working%20on%20these%20thorny%20deals%20that%20were%20scrutinized%20on%20both%20sides%20of%20the%20aisle%20took%20great%20finesse.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDan%20is%20the%20consummate%20CEO%2C%26quot%3B%20another%20former%20managing%20director%20said.%20%26quot%3BHe%20is%20going%20to%20be%20a%20CEO%20somewhere%20if%20he%20doesn't%20get%20this%20job.%20It%20just%20won't%20be%20at%20Morgan%20Stanley.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3ESUBSCRIBE%20TO%20READ%20THE%20FULL%20STORY%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdan-simkowitz-morgan-stanley-james-gorman-succession-2023-10%5C%22%3EThis%20Morgan%20Stanley%20veteran%20is%20ready%20to%20be%20CEO%20%E2%80%94%20it%20just%20might%20be%20somewhere%20else%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EAndy%20Saperstein%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESaperstein%20followed%20Gorman%2C%20his%20boss%20at%20McKinsey%20and%20Merrill%20Lynch%2C%20to%20Morgan%20Stanley%20in%202006%2C%C2%A0while%20Pick%20and%20Simkowitz%20have%20each%20spent%20more%20than%20three%20decades%20at%20the%20bank.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Staten%20Island%20native%2C%20who%20prefe