Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20letters%20came%20after%20the%20%3Cem%3EWashington%20Post%3C%2Fem%3E%20published%20a%20series%20of%20reports%20which%20claimed%20that%20Facebook%2C%20WhatsApp%2C%20and%20YouTube%20had%20failed%20to%20control%20communal%20and%20Hindutva%20content%2C%20often%20generated%20by%20those%20associated%20%E2%80%93%20either%20directly%20or%20loosely%20%E2%80%93%20with%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECiting%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EPost%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20report%20titled%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fworld%2F2023%2F09%2F26%2Findia-monu-manesar-viligante-social-media%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CHe%20live-streamed%20his%20attacks%20on%20Indian%20Muslims.%20YouTube%20gave%20him%20an%20award%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20about%20the%20role%20of%20YouTube%20in%20%E2%80%9Cpropagating%20communal%20hatred%20and%20dividing%20the%20country%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20letter%20to%20Pichai%20said%20that%20Google%20and%20specifically%20YouTube%20is%20culpable%20of%20abetting%20social%20disharmony%20and%20inciting%20communal%20hatred%20in%20India.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CFurther%20we%20have%20data%20that%20shows%20algorithmic%20moderation%20and%20suppression%20of%20opposition%20leaders%E2%80%99%20content%20on%20your%20platform%20while%20also%20promoting%20ruling%20party%20content%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20letter%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CSuch%20blatant%20partisanship%20and%20bias%20towards%20one%20political%20formation%20by%20a%20private%20foreign%20company%20is%20tantamount%20to%20interfering%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20democracy%2C%20one%20that%20we%20in%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20cannot%20but%20take%20seriously.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EKarnataka%20minister%20and%20Congress%20leader%20Priyank%20Kharge%20also%20accused%20Yo