%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20name%20of%20the%20rail%20service%20was%20changed%20from%20RapidX%20to%20NaMo%20Bharat%20yesterday.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%2017-km%20priority%20section%20of%20the%20Delhi-Ghaziabad-Meerut%20RRTS%20Corridor%20will%20open%20for%20passengers%20from%20tomorrow%2C%20a%20day%20after%20its%20inauguration.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20priority%20section%2C%20between%20Sahibabad%20and%20Duhai%20Depot%2C%20has%20five%20stations%20--%20Sahibabad%2C%20Ghaziabad%2C%20Guldhar%2C%20Duhai%20and%20Duhai%20Depot.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERRTS%20trains%20prioritise%20passenger%20comfort%20with%20features%20like%20overhead%20storage%2C%20Wi-Fi%2C%20and%20charging%20options%20at%20each%20seat.%20Moreover%2C%20there%20will%20be%20a%20premium-class%20car%20with%20spacious%20seating%2C%20ample%20legroom%2C%20and%20coat%20hangers%2C%20a%20press%20release%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECCTV%20cameras%2C%20an%20emergency%20door-opening%20mechanism%20and%20a%20button%20to%20communicate%20with%20a%20train%20operator%20are%20among%20the%20safety%20features%20of%20this%20train.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Delhi-Ghaziabad-Meerut%20corridor%20is%20being%20developed%20at%20a%20cost%20of%20more%20than%20Rs%2030%2C000%20crore%20and%20will%20connect%20Delhi%20to%20Meerut%20with%20a%20travel%20time%20of%20less%20than%20an%20hour%20through%20urban%20centres%20of%20Ghaziabad%2C%20Muradnagar%20and%20Modinagar%2C%20the%20PMO%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697794620000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fg9u3p2tg_pm-modi_625x300_20_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-modi-inaugurates-namo-bharat-indias-1st-regional-rapid-train-service-4498814%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20today%20flagged%20off%20'Namo%20Bharat'%2C%20India's%20first%20semi-high%20speed%20regional%20rail%20service%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A23%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2