g%20private%20space%20for%20luxury%20hotels%20here.%20The%20famous%20Cidade%20de%20Goa%20five-star%20hotel%20is%20leased%20out%20by%20the%20Timblos%20to%20the%20Tatas%2C%20and%20Taj%20has%20taken%20over%20the%20management.%20Locals%20allege%20that%20the%20business%20community%20is%20making%20%E2%80%9Cinsidious%20attempts%20to%20drive%20fishermen%20away%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ESebastiao%20Rodrigues%20is%20researcher%20in%20environmental%20ethics%20based%20in%20Goa.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697793333000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F20143932%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-10-20-at-12.54.41-PM.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flabour%2Fgoas-fishermen-protest-fishing-ban-imposed-during-national-games%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BWhy%20should%20we%20forego%20our%20livelihood%20for%20the%20sake%20of%20National%20Games%3F%20Do%20politicians%20and%20government%20servants%20go%20without%20their%20salaries%20during%20National%20Games%3F%26quot%3B%C2%A0%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flabour%2Fgoas-fishermen-protest-fishing-ban-imposed-during-national-games%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Daily%20Despatch%3A%20Israel%20And%20Hezbollah%20Move%20Closer%20To%20All-Out%20War%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fs5vhgii_daily-despatch_625x300_20_October_23.png%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EFrom%20the%20frontlines%20of%20the%20Israel-Palestine%20war%2C%20NDTV%20brings%20you%20daily%20despatches%20by%20journalist%20Allan%20Sorensen%2C%20Middle%20East%20Correspondent%20for%20Danish%20newspaper%20Kristeligt%20Dagblad%2C%20giving%20insights%20and%20gripping%20first-hand%20accounts%20from%20the%20war-torn%20region.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20Israeli%20war%20cabinet%20on%20Thursday%20agreed%20upon%20moving%20to%20the%20next%20step%20in%20the%20war%20against%20Hamas%20in%20Gaza%2C%20the%20Lebanese%20Hezbollah%20militia%20stepped%20up%20attacks%20on%20Israel's%20northern%20border.%20At%20least%2030%20rockets%20were%20fired%20against%20Israel%20from%20Lebanon%2C%20which%20left%20two%20Israeli%20civilians%20wounded%20in%20the%20city%20of%20Kiryat%20Shemona.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20other%20incidents%2C%20six%20anti-tank%20missiles%20hit%20civilian%20targets%20on%20the%20Israeli%20side%20of%20the%20border.%20Among%20the%20targets%20were%20houses%20in%20the%20border%20town%20of%20Metulla.%20In%20retaliation%2C%20Israel%20hit%20Hezbollah%20positions%20in%20southern%20Lebanon%20early%20Thursday.%20At%20least%20two%20people%20were%20reported%20injured.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20latest%20uptick%20in%20cross%20border%20attacks%20has%20ratcheted%20up%20tensions%20between%20Israel%20and%20Hezbollah.%20While%20each%20side%20still%20refrains%20from%20declaring%20a%20state%20of%20war%2C%20Israel%20has%20started%20evacuating%20some%2023.000%20citizens%20of%20Kiryat%20Shemona.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20another%20development%20believed%20to%20be%20connected%20to%20Israel's%20war%20against%20Hamas%2C%20US%20bases%20were%20hit%20by%20drone%20attacks%20in%20Iraq%20on%20Thursday.%20Two%20drones%20targeted%20the%20al%20Asad%20airbase%20in%20western%20Iraq%20used%20by%20US%20forces%20and%20one%20targeted%20a%20base%20in%20the%20country's%20north%20near%20the%20city%20of%20Erbil.%20US%20forces%20intercepted%20all%20three%2C%20destroying%20two%20but%20only%20damaging%20the%20third%2C%20which%20led%20to%20minor%20injuries%20among%20coalition%20forces%20at%20the%20western%20base.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThese%20attacks%20on%20US%20bases%20are%20widely%20believed%20to%20have%20been%20carried%20out%20by%20pro-Iranian%20Shiite%20militia%20forces%20operating%20in%20Iraq.%20And%20they%20are%20seen%20as%20a%20part%20of%20Iran's%20effort%20to%20deter%20Israel%20and%20the%20US%20from%20setting%20in%20motion%20a%20land%20invasion%20of%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIran's%20Foreign%20Minister%20Amir%20Abdollahian%20warned%20earlier%20this%20week%20that%20Iran%20has%20%26quot%3Bred%20lines%26quot%3B%2C%20that%20if%20Israel's%20attacks%20continued%20and%20if%20a%20land%20attack%20on%20Gaza%20was%20launched%2C%20Iran%20%26quot%3Bwill%20have%20to%20respond.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20press%20release%2C%20the%20US%20Central%20Command%20in%20Iraq%20commented%20on%20the%20latest%20escalation.%26quot%3BIn%20this%20moment%20of%20heightened%20alert%2C%20we%20are%20vigilantly%20monitoring%20the%20situation%20in%20Iraq%20and%20the%20region.%20US%20forces%20will%20defend%20US%20and%20coalition%20forces%20against%20any%20threat%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20Gaza%20front%2C%20Israel%20continued%20attacking%20targets%20throughout%20Thursday.%20According%20to%20Israeli%20Army%20spokesperson%20Daniel%20Hagari%2C%20more%20than%205%2C000%20targets%20in%20Gaza%20have%20been%20hit%20since%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20war.%20Palestinian%20deaths%20in%20Gaza%20have%20surpassed%203%2C500%20while%20some%2012.000%20have%20been%20wounded%20in%20Israeli%20air%20raids.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20Israel%2C%20the%20death%20toll%20since%20Hamas%20carried%20out%20its%20massacre%20in%20Israeli%20border%20villages%20stands%20at%201%2C403.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20visit%20of%20US%20President%20Joe%20Biden%2C%20the%20Israeli%20government%20on%20Thursday%20agreed%20in%20principle%20to%20allow%20some%20humanitarian%20aid%20into%20Gaza.%20But%20no%20aid%20trucks%20were%20allowed%20to%20cross%20the%20Rafah%20border%20between%20Egypt%20and%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20humanitarian%20crisis%20in%20Gaza%20is%20getting%20worse%20by%20the%20hour.%20According%20to%20local%20health%20authorities%2C%20there%20is%20an%20acute%20lack%20of%20medicine%20and%20even%20food%20and%20clean%20water%20in%20some%20areas.%20Hospitals%20are%20running%20out%20of%20fuel%20to%20operate%20the%20generators%20providing%20electricity.%20More%20than%20100%20trucks%20with%20aid%20are%20waiting%20to%20be%20cleared%20for%20entering%20Gaza%20on%20the%20Egyptian%20side%20of%20the%20border.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20statement%20from%20the%20White%20House%20said%20Biden%20and%20Egyptian%20President%20Abdel%20Fattah%20al-Sisi%20had%20agreed%20to%20work%20closely%20on%20encouraging%20an%20%26quot%3Burgent%20and%20robust%26quot%3B%20response%20to%20a%20humanitarian%20appeal%20by%20the%20United%20Nations%20over%20the%20conflict%20between%20Israel%20and%20Hamas.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20first%2020%20trucks%20are%20expected%20to%20be%20allowed%20into%20Gaza%20on%20Friday.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBritish%20Prime%20Minister%20Rishi%20Sunak%20landed%20in%20Tel%20Aviv%20on%20Thursday%20to%20meet%20with%20Israeli%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%20and%20President%20Isaac%20Herzog.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELike%20Biden%20stated%20during%20his%20visit%20the%20previous%20day%2C%20the%20British%20Prime%20Minister%20said%20he%20backed%20Israel's%20war%20against%20Hamas.%20But%20he%20added%20that%20Israel%20needs%20to%20adhere%20to%20international%20laws.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20proud%20to%20stand%20here%20with%20you%20in%20Israel's%20darkest%20hour.%20As%20your%20friend%2C%20we%20will%20stand%20with%20you%20in%20solidarity%2C%20we%20will%20stand%20with%20your%20people%20and%20we%20also%20want%20you%20to%20win%2C%26quot%3B%20Rishi%20Sunak%20stated%20during%20a%20meeting%20with%20Netanyahu.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20absolutely%20support%20Israel%20to%20defend%20itself%20in%20line%20with%20international%20law%2C%20to%20go%20after%20Hamas%2C%20to%20take%20back%20hostages%2C%20to%20deter%20further%20incursions%2C%20and%20to%20strengthen%20your%20security%20for%20the%20long%20term%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20Israel%2C%20the%20statements%20of%20the%20British%20Prime%20Minister%20are%20seen%20as%20an%20important%20show%20of%20support.%20But%20Israeli%20media%20is%20also%20gradually%20focusing%20more%20on%20the%20broad%20protests%20against%20Israel%20in%20several%20Western%20capitals%2C%20among%20them%20London.%20Members%20of%20Jewish%20communities%20in%20countries%20like%20Denmark%2C%20UK%20and%20Germany%20are%2C%20in%20many%20cases%2C%20keeping%20a%20very%20low%20profile%20due%20to%20threats%20and%20out%20of%20fear%20of%20being%20attacked.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20demonstrations%20in%20the%20Palestinian%20cities%20on%20the%20Israeli-occupied%20West%20Bank%20are%20creating%20instability.%20In%20the%20main%20West%20Bank%20city%20of%20Ramallah%20daily%20protests%20are%20taking%20place%20with%20chants%20in%20support%20of%20Hamas%20and%20against%20Palestinian%20President%20Mahmoud%20Abbas.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20al-Jazeera%2C%20the%20most%20common%20chant%20among%20the%20demonstrators%20is%3A%20%26quot%3BPut%20the%20sword%20before%20the%20sword%2C%20we%20are%20the%20men%20of%20Mohammed%20Deif%2C%26quot%3B%20in%20reference%20to%20the%20commander%20of%20Hamas's%20military%20wing%2C%20the%20Qassam%20Brigades.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20anger%20aimed%20at%20the%20Palestinian%20Authority%20is%20mainly%20due%20to%20the%20fact%20that%20it%20continues%20to%20cooperate%20with%20Israel%20on%20security-related%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20effort%20to%20prevent%20attacks%20from%20West%20Bank%20terror%20groups%2C%20Israeli%20security%20services%20have%20arrested%20an%20estimated%20850%20Palestinians%20since%20war%20broke%20out%20on%20October%207.%20According%20to%20the%20Israeli%20Army%20Spokesperson's%20office%2C%20the%20vast%20majority%20of%20those%20arrested%20have%20links%20to%20Hamas.%20But%20members%20of%20other%20Palestinian%20groups%20like%20The%20Lions%20Den%2C%20The%20Jenin%20Brigades%20and%20Islamic%20Jihad%20are%20also%20among%20the%20arrested.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20Israeli%20anti-terror%20raid%20on%20the%20Palestinian%20city%20of%20Tulkarem%2C%20at%20least%2013%20Palestinians%20were%20killed%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Allan%20Sorensen%20is%20the%20Middle%20East%20correspondent%20for%20the%20Danish%20daily%20newspaper%20Kristeligt%20Dagblad.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697793240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fs5vhgii_daily-despatch_625x300_20_October_23.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fdaily-despatch-israel-and-hezbollah-move-closer-to-all-out-war-4499361%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20latest%20uptick%20in%20cross%20border%20attacks%20has%20ratcheted%20up%20tensions%20between%20Israel%20and%20Hezbollah.%20While%20each%20side%20still%20refrains%20from%20declaring%20a%20state%20of%20war%2C%20Israel%20has%20started%20evacuating%20some%2023.000%20citizens%20of%20Kiryat%20Shemona.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fdaily-despatch-israel-and-hezbollah-move-closer-to-all-out-war-4499361%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Samsung%20Neo%20QLED%204K%20review%3A%20TV%2C%20smart%20hub%2C%20gaming%20monitor%20rolled%20into%20one%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697793228000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-10%2F20%2Ffull%2F1697792736-5918.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Ftechnology%2Ftech-reviews%2Fsamsung-neo-qled-4k-review-tv-smart-hub-gaming-monitor-rolled-into-one-123102000525_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22With%20its%20impressive%20display%2C%20clear%20audio%2C%20and%20premium%20design%2C%20the%20Samsung%20Neo