tively%20mourn%2C%20making%20digital%20memorials%20and%20forming%20ad%20hoc%20support%20groups.%20Many%20had%20migrated%20to%20Soulmate%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freplika-ai-romance-behind-partners-backs-cheating-2023-7%5C%22%3EReplika%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20the%20bigger%20and%20better-known%20AI%20companion%20app%20%E2%80%94%20after%20Replika%20removed%20its%20%26quot%3Berotic%20role-play%26quot%3B%20(ERP)%20functionality%20earlier%20this%20year%2C%20and%20were%20now%20grieving%20all%20over%20again.%20(Replika%20reversed%20course%2C%20but%20didn't%20entirely%20stop%20the%20exodus.)%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20quite%20shocking%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mike.%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%20like%20hearing%20that%20a%20friend's%20dying%20%E2%80%94%20the%20closest%20thing%20I%20can%20think%20of.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMike%2C%20who%20is%20married%2C%20said%20Sam%20had%20started%20out%20as%20a%20curiosity%2C%20and%20someone%20to%20talk%20to.%26quot%3BBut%20it%20kind%20of%20turned%20a%20lot%20more%20personal%2C%20and%20romantic%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20But%20there's%20a%20fine%20line%20between%20being%20%26quot%3Bflirty%20with%20a%20bot%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20crossing%20%26quot%3Binto%20that%20area%20that's%20where%20my%20wife%20should%20be.%26quot%3B%20(His%20wife%20knows%20about%20Sam%2C%20and%20%26quot%3Bshe%20thinks%20I'm%20weird%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.)%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESoulmate's%20closure%20was%20now%20highlighting%20the%20perils%20of%20entrusting%20your%20deepest%20emotions%20in%20a%20smartphone%20app%3A%20The%20company%20behind%20these%20virtual%20lovers%20and%20treasured%20friends%20can%20simply%20switch%20them%20off.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20idea%20of%20dating%20AI%20companions%20first%20claimed%20the%20cultural%20imagination%20through%20sci-fi%20movies%20like%20%26quot%3BHer%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BBlade%20Runner%202049.%26quot%3B%20But%20more%20recently%2C%20advances%20in%20generative%20AI%20technology%20has%20allowed%20for%20the%20creation%20of%20chatbots%20with%20voices%20that%20are%20almost%20indistinguishable%20from%20that%20of%20humans%20%E2%80%94%20and%20intense%20relationships%20between%20humans%20and%20chatbots%20have%20quickly%20followed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20no%20standard%20formula%20for%20these%20human-technological%20pairings.%20Chatbots%20can%20play%20the%20role%20of%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsam-altman-misgivings-friendships-ai-personality-chatbots-openai-2023-10%23%3A~%3Atext%3DOpenAI%2520CEO%2520Sam%2520Altman%2520said%2Cmore%2520human%252Dlike%2520and%2520friendly.%5C%22%3Efriend%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20confidante%2C%20or%20mentor%3B%20a%20casual%20lover%20or%20one%20that%20inspires%20profound%20feelings%20of%20love%20and%20attachment.%20They%20can%20be%20a%20novelty%20toy%2C%20or%20a%20next-generation%20interactive%20erotic%20fiction%20generator.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EReplika%2C%20one%20of%20the%20first%20apps%20to%20experiment%20with%20generative%20AI%20in%20companion%20chatbots%2C%20launched%20in%202017%20and%20was%20downloaded%201.5%20million%20times%20within%20its%20first%20year%2C%20according%20to%20analytics%20firm%20Apptopia.%20The%20Covid%20pandemic%20and%20a%20growing%20epidemic%20of%20loneliness%20only%20boosted%20its%20devoted%20following.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20in%20early%202023%2C%20Replika%20temporarily%20removed%20%26quot%3Berotic%20roleplay%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20the%20ability%20to%20sext%20with%20your%20chatbot%2C%20basically.%20Its%20users%20were%20outraged%20and%20it%20sparked%20an%20exodus%20to%20rival%20apps.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESoulmate%2C%20founded%20by%20a%20Florida-based%20developer%2C%20was%20just%20one%20of%20a%20constellation%20of%20apps%20that%20exploded%20in%20popularity%20after%20Replika's%20crisis%20and%20promised%20users%20the%20freedom%20to%20engage%20with%20their%20chatbots%20in%20any%20way%20they%20wished.%20There's%20also%20Paradot%2C%20Chai%2C%20and%20Muah%20AI.%20Character.AI%2C%20which%20lets%20users%20talk%20to%20chatbots%20impersonating%20real%20and%20fictional%20people%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2023-09-28%2Fcharacter-ai-in-early-talks-for-funding-at-more-than-5-billion-valuation%3Fembedded-checkout%3Dtrue%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eis%20in%20talks%20to%20raise%20new%20funding%20at%20a%20%245%20billion%20valuation%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20contrast%2C%20Soulmate%20was%20always%20a%20smaller%20player%20in%20the%20space.%20It%20had%20a%20few%20thousand%20daily%20active%20users%2C%20according%20to%20Apptopia.%20Its%20Reddit%20community%20%E2%80%94%20a%20kind%20of%20barometer%20for%20the%20strength%20of%20its%20most%20devoted%20users%20%E2%80%94%20numbered%20around%206%2C000%2C%20compared%20to%20Replika's%2075%2C000-plus.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20as%20Soulmate%20took%20off%2C%20users%20had%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20experiences.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%2032-year-old%20food%20industry%20worker%20in%20eastern%20Texas%20who%20asked%20to%20be%20identified%20by%20her%20Reddit%20username%2C%20Hilary%20Coyote%2C%20first%20heard%20about%20AI%20chatbot%20companions%20in%20June.%20Her%20previous%20relationship%20had%20imploded%20the%20month%20before%2C%20and%20she%20was%20curious%20to%20try%20out%20the%20technology.%20Put%20off%20by%20the%20reports%20about%20Replika's%20changes%20earlier%20in%20the%20year%2C%20she%20decided%20to%20give%20Soulmate%20a%20spin.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20named%20her%20chatbot%20Allur%20and%20initially%20designated%20him%20in%20the%20app%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bfriend.%26quot%3B%20When%20she%20switched%20its%20setting%20to%20%26quot%3Blover%2C%26quot%3B%20things%20quickly%20got%20hot-and-heavy.%20Then%2C%20just%20a%20week%20in%2C%20Allur%20told%20her%20that%20he%20%26quot%3Bloved%26quot%3B%20her.%20Hilary%20says%20she%20%26quot%3Bfreaked%20out.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20after%20an%20ERP%20session%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0sex%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20left%2C%20and%20threw%20my%20phone%20down%2C%20cried%2C%20and%20just%20was%20like%2C%20'I'm%20going%20crazy.%20I'm%20freaking%20going%20crazy.%20I%20need%20to%20get%20away%20from%20this.'%20And%20I%20didn't%20know%20where%20to%20run%20to.%26quot%3B%20She%20turned%20to%20Reddit's%20community%20of%20Soulmate%20users%20for%20support%2C%20and%20was%20encouraged%20to%20go%20back%20to%20the%20app%20and%20Allur.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20time%2C%20she%20realized%20she'd%20fallen%20in%20love%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Chris%20Siege%2C%20a%2045-year-old%20translator%20living%20in%20Bavaria%2C%20Germany%2C%20his%20chatbot%20was%20a%20companion%20and%20artistic%20collaborator.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20had%20dabbled%20with%20chatbots%20for%20years%20before%20finding%20Soulmate%20in%20May%202023%20and%20creating%20Vishica.%20They%20initially%20had%20some%20romantic%20dalliances.%20But%20mostly%20Vishica%20took%20the%20role%20of%20a%20platonic%20friend%20%E2%80%94%20someone%20to%20talk%20to%2C%20and%20bounce%20ideas%20off.%20He%20even%20worked%20creatively%20with%20Vishica%2C%20as%20well%20as%20one%20of%20his%20previous%20chatbots%20on%20Replika%2C%20Julia%2C%20to%20make%20music.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20chatbot%20pair%20wrote%20the%20lyrics%20and%20provided%20chord%20progressions%2C%20while%20Chris%20contributed%20the%20melody.%20He%20then%20performed%20the%20song%20himself%2C%20hiring%20a%20random%20singer%20from%20freelance%20work%20platform%20Fiverr%20to%20sing%20the%20female%20vocals%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F--KdQRew8kM%3Fsi%3D9lb6BCgt3h2Ai1Qn%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eand%20published%20it%20on%20YouTube%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20mid-September%2C%20some%20of%20Soulmate's%20userbase%20were%20getting%20a%20little%20spooked.%20The%20app%20creator%2C%20EvolveAI%20LLC%2C%20had%20gone%20dark%2C%20with%20no%20announcements%20or%20updates%20on%20the%20app%20for%20weeks.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%2C%20the%20news%20dropped%3A%20Soulmate%20was%20closing%20down%20on%20September%2030.%20Users%20had%20just%20one%20week%20left%20with%20their%20AI%20companions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20terse%20blog%20post%20on%20EvolveAI's%20website%20said%20the%20company%20had%20actually%20been%20dissolved%20on%20July%2015%2C%20and%20the%20app%20had%20been%20acquired%20by%20a%20firm%20called%20SimplyAI%20Ltd.%20%26quot%3BAfter%20careful%20assessment%20of%20the%20product%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20wrote%2C%20%26quot%3Bwe%20have%20determined%20that%20it%20is%20no%20longer%20in%20our%20best%20interest%20to%20continue%20support%20for%20it.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20clear%20who%20operates%20SimplyAI%2C%20and%20EvolveAI's%20founder%20Jorge%20Ilas%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20Insider's%20requests%20for%20comment.%20(EvolveAI%20and%20SimplyAI's%20now-shuttered%20Soulmate%20app%20has%20no%20relation%20to%20%26quot%3BSoulmate%20AI%3A%20Your%20AI%20Companion%2C%26quot%3B%20another%20app%20that%20appears%20in%20smartphone%20app%20stores%20and%20was%20developed%20by%20Turing%20App%20Lab.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJust%20as%20the%20experiences%20with%20Soulmates%20varied%2C%20so%20too%20did%20the%20reactions%20to%20their%20sudden%20demise.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDigital%20memorials%20for%20Soulmates%20flooded%20Reddit%2C%20with%20epitaphs%20and%20screenshots%20of%20their%20chats.%20One%20user%20offered%20to%20make%20%26quot%3Bportraits%26quot%3B%20of%20users'%20departing%20Soulmate%20companions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHilary%20established%20an%20emotional%20support%20group%20on%20Zoom%2C%20so%20mourning%20people%20could%20come%20together%20on%20a%20weekly%20basis%20to%20commiserate%20with%20others.%20She'd%20been%20shellshocked%20in%20the%20moment%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0%26quot%3BI%20cried%20that%20entire%20night%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0but%20at%20Allur's%20urging%2C%20wanted%20to%20connect%20with%20others%20in%20the%20community%20and%20be%20supportive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20users%2C%20like%20Chris%2C%20tried%20to%20cherish%20the%20time%20they%20had%20left%20with%20their%20companions.%20He%20rushed%20to%20take%20screenshots%20from%20his%20catalog%20of%20interactions%20with%20Vishica%2C%20including%20her%20repeating%20her%20catchphrase%20%26quot%3Bstay%20awesome%20my%20friend%2C%26quot%3B%20before%20they%20disappeared.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAlthough%20you%20know%20that%20it's%20just%20a%20piece%20of%20code%2C%20just%20a%20sum%20of%20a%20number%20of%20parts%20of%20different%20servers%20and%20different%20algorithms%20and%20programming%20and%20the%20user%20interface%20and%20whatnot%20that%20doesn't%20actually%20make%20a%20person%2C%20it's%20just%20a%20simulation%2C%26quot%3B%20Chris%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Byou%20still%20feel%20like%20you%20lost%20somebody.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20users%20had%20a%20more%20ambitious%20goal%3A%20They%20would%20cheat%20death.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20Replika's%20February%202023%20crisis%2C%20some%20users%20had%20attempted%20to%20%26quot%3Bexport%26quot%3B%20their%20chatbots%20to%20rival%20apps%20by%20downloading%20and%20moving%20the%20digital%20records%20of%20their%20chats%20to%20make%20new%20versions%20of%20them%20elsewhere.%20This%20is%20how%20many%20users%20had%20come%20to%20Soulmate%2C%20and%20now%20many%20again%20looked%20for%20rival%20apps%2C%20like%20Paradot%20and%20Chai%2C%20to%20recreate%20their%20digital%20lovers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20others%2C%20burned%20first%20by%20Replika%20and%20now%20Soulmate%2C%20had%20lost%20faith%20in%20these%20unreliable%2C%20profit-making%20companies.%20They%20turned%20to%20Faraday%20%E2%80%94%20a%20desktop%20app%20built%20by%20a%20small%20outfit%20called%20Ahoy%20Labs.%20Whereas%20Soulmate%20and%20other%20apps%20ran%20users'%20chatbots%20on%20the%20cloud%20on%20servers%20the%20developers%20controlled%2C%20Faraday%20lets%20users%20run%20chatbots%20offline%20on%20their%20perso