ments%20from%20the%20Nizam%20era%20that%20recognise%20them%20as%20Kunbis%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20this%20solution%20was%20not%20accepted%20by%20Patil%20and%20his%20supporters.%20On%20October%2014%2C%20the%20maratha%20leader%20gave%20a%20deadline%20to%20the%20state%20government%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theweek.in%2Fwire-updates%2Fnational%2F2023%2F10%2F14%2Fbom6-mh-maratha-quota-jarange.html%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CAfter%20October%2024%2C%20it%20will%20be%20either%20my%20funeral%20procession%20or%20the%20community%E2%80%99s%20victory%20celebration%20(after%20granting%20of%20reservation).%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20activist%20said%20he%20would%20address%20the%20community%20on%20October%2022%20to%20explain%20their%20course%20of%20action%20after%20October%2024%20in%20case%20the%20demand%20is%20not%20fulfilled.%20He%20also%20asked%20his%20supporters%20to%20maintain%20peace%20during%20protests%2C%20%3Cem%3EPTI%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theweek.in%2Fwire-updates%2Fnational%2F2023%2F10%2F14%2Fbom6-mh-maratha-quota-jarange.html%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697790650000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F30123722%2FIllustration-Pariplab-Chakraborty.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fmaratha-quota-stir-man-dies-by-suicide-leaves-note-demanding-reservation-for-community%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22His%20death%20comes%20just%20five%20days%20before%20the%20deadline%20set%20by%20Maratha%20leader%20Manoj%20Jarange%20Patil%20who%20has%20threatened%20a%20wider%20agitation%20if%20the%20Marathas%20were%20not%20recognised%20as%20OBCs%20by%20October%2024.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fmaratha-quota-stir-man-dies-by-suicide-leaves-note-demanding-reservation-for-community%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%2