%2F2023%2F10%2F20114909%2Fimage0-225x300.jpeg%20225w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F20114909%2Fimage0-768x1024.jpeg%20768w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-680962%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ERati%20Bhan%20ji%2C%20a%20plumber%20since%201996%2C%20says%20to%20be%20able%20to%20work%20on%20site%2C%20independently%2C%20a%20plumber%20needs%20five%20years%20of%20training%20mixed%20with%20experience.%20Photo%20provided%20by%20author.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20had%20returned%20from%20Singapore%2C%20triggering%20class%20arrogance%20in%20me.%20He%20was%20on%20training%2C%20funded%20by%20a%20pipe%20company%20that%20wanted%20to%20put%20him%20in%20charge%20of%20a%20project%20in%20Mumbai.%20The%20training%20was%20not%20part%20of%20the%20Skill%20India%20mission%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pmkvyofficial.org%2F%5C%22%3EPradhan%20Mantri%20Kaushal%20Vikas%20Yojana%3C%2Fa%3E.%20This%20was%20not%20a%20wasteful%20two-month%20course%20for%20newbies%2C%20ill-suited%20to%20take%20the%20rough%20and%20tumble%20of%20plumbing%2C%20who%20will%20drop%20out%20of%20the%20trade%20in%20no%20time.%20Out%20of%20ten%20plumbers%2C%20less%20than%20two%20trained%20by%20Skill%20India%20stick%20around%2C%20practitioners%20who%20source%20from%20the%20mission%20told%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Singapore%20stint%20was%20training%20in%20best%20practices%20for%20Rati%20Bhan%20ji%2C%20who%20has%20been%20a%20plumber%20since%201996.%20He%20works%20on%20site%20with%20a%20team%20of%20senior%20and%20junior%20masons%2C%20and%20helpers%2C%20and%20labour.%20He%20is%20so%20experienced%20that%20he%20can%20detect%2C%20even%20from%20a%20description%20over%20the%20phone%2C%20where%20his%20team%20is%20getting%20stuck.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20kind%20of%20training%20is%20not%20provided%20in%20the%20Skill%20India%20syllabi.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20Plumbing%20Association%20told%20me%20the%20correct%20way%20of%20training%20new%20plumbers%3A%20it%20should%20be%20a%20modular%20course%20consisting%20of%20at%20least%20eight%20modules%2C%20stretching%20over%2015%20days%20each.%20The%20modules%20should%20not%20be%20taught%20in%20continuity%20because%20plumbers%2C%20after%20all%2C%20have%20to%20earn%20between%20their%20training.%20The%20spaced-modules%20programme%20also%20lets%20the%20job%20market%20test%20out%20a%20plumber%E2%80%99s%20stickability.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERati%20Bhan%20ji%20feels%20that%20while%20he%20can%20train%20an%20apprentice%20in%20a%20month%20to%20do%20plumbing%20of%20a%20basic%20bathroom%2C%20anything%20more%20will%20need%20a%20year.%20And%20to%20emerge%20as%20a%20plumber%20who%20can%20do%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3Ebade%20se%20bada%20kaam%20and%20chote%20se%20chota%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0or%20in%20other%20words%2C%20work%20on%20a%20site%2C%20will%20take%20five%20years%20of%20training%20mixed%20with%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENot%20sticking%20around%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20against%20this%2C%20Skill%20India%20tries%20to%20prepare%20a%20plumber%20in%20two%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERohit%20Jadhav%2C%20who%20runs%20Swastik%20Plumbing%20and%20Home%20Services%20in%20Pune%2C%20said%20plumbing%20is%20a%20rough%20trade%20and%20new%20recruits%20simply%20give%20up%20and%20leave.%20Both%20Jadhav%20and%20Rati%20Bhan%20ji%20estimate%20that%20less%20than%2020%25%20of%20those%20entering%20the%20plumbing%20trade%20stick%20with%20it%20for%20the%20long%20term.%20India%E2%80%99s%20high%20and%20mounting%20heatwaves%20make%20it%20extremely%20difficult%20for%20a%20trade%20to%20be%20practised%20largely%20in%20the%20open.%20In%20addition%2C%20the%20Indian%20companies%E2%80%99%20reluctance%20to%20provide%20basic%20equipment%20such%20as%20helmets%20and%20shoes%20to%20plumbers%20make%20it%20even%20more%20challenging.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20heat%2C%20a%20bathroom%20can%20become%20a%20furnace.%20This%20generation%20also%20wants%20to%20s