%E2%80%99%20names%20are%20sometimes%20common%2C%20and%20sometimes%20not.%20PMKVY%20is%20described%20as%20the%20flagship%20scheme%20of%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Skill%20Development%20and%20Entrepreneurship%2C%20implemented%20by%20NSDC.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flabour%2Findia-narendra-modi-jobs-unemployment%5C%22%3EThree%20Claims%20of%20Government%20Economists%20About%20Jobs%20Put%20to%20the%20Test%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EApprenticeships%20and%20contracts%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20don%E2%80%99t%20consider%20apprenticeships%20as%20placements.%20%3Cem%3EEk%20saal%20main%20mera%20baccha%20to%20vapas%20sarak%20pe%20aa%20gaya%3C%2Fem%3E%20(my%20candidate%20is%20back%20to%20being%20unemployed%20in%20a%20year)%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Umesh%20Gautam%2C%20who%2C%20in%20roles%20as%20wide%20ranging%20as%20a%20placement%20officer%20or%20in-charge%20of%20a%20whole%20skill%20centre%2C%20has%20placed%20skilled%20candidates%20with%20companies%20for%20the%20past%20two%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F20115441%2Fimage-1415.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22971%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F20115441%2Fimage-1415.png%20971w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F20115441%2Fimage-1415-300x214.png%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-680964%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22692%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EUmesh%20Gautam%2C%20with%20two%20decades%20of%20experience%20in%20connecting%20skilled%20workers%20with%20companies%2C%20emphasizes%20that%20an%20apprenticeship%20should%20not%20be%20categorised%20as%20a%20job%20placement%20and%20should%20be%20excluded%20from%20placement%20data.%20Photo%20provided%20by%20author.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EApprenticeships%20which%20last%20a%20year%20is%20a%20carrot%20companies%20dangle%20in%20front%20of%20skilled%20candidates%2C%20he%20said.%20Once%20a%20year%20is%20over%2C%20apprentices%20are%20chucked%20out%20into%20the%20cold.%20Now%20comes%20the%20second%20carrot.%20Desperate%20skilled%20candidates%20see%20their%20earnings%20dip%20from%20Rs%2025%2C000%20a%20month%20to%20zero.%20They%20are%20directed%20towards%20labour%20contractors%20for%20India%20Inc.%20The%20riders%3A%20sub-contracted%20employment%2C%20no%20insurance%2C%20no%20graded%20pay%20hikes%2C%20no%20job%20security.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20%E2%80%9Ccasualisation%E2%80%9D%20of%20employment%2C%20or%20an%20increase%20in%20%E2%80%98on%20contract%E2%80%99%20workers%20%E2%80%93%20and%20their%20insecure%20working%20conditions%20%E2%80%93%20led%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Fgurgaon%2Fmaruti-factory-violence-verdict-a-brief-history-of-the-case%2Fstory-hXMxAHf6I3DuJHCflV47YN.html%23%3A~%3Atext%3DJuly%252018%252C%25202012%253A%2520A%2520mob%2Ctwo%2520Japanese%2520officials%252C%2520were%2520injured.%5C%22%3E2012%20strike%20in%20Maruti%2C%20which%20resulted%20in%20the%20death%20of%20a%20manager.%3C%2Fa%3E%20That%20strike%20itself%20was%20used%20to%20further%20hire%20workers%20on%20contract.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Fwhy-is-india-inc-reluctant-to-participate-in-the-skill-india-campaign%5C%22%3EWhy%20Is%20India%20Inc%20Reluctant%20to%20Participate%20in%20the%20Skill%20India%20Campaign%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESanjay%20Srivastava%2C%20a%20sociologist%2C%20who%20is%20now%20at%20SOAS%2C%20University%20of%20London%2C%20but%20earlier%20taught%20at%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20University%20and%20visited%20the%20homes%20of%20some%20of%20the%20147%20jailed%20Maruti%20workers%2C%20had%20told%20me%20in%202015%3A%20%E2%80%9C(We%20need)%20an%20industrial%20climate%20which%20is%20fair%2C%20which%20has%20long-term%20sustainability%20and%20some%20amount%20of%20stability.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20a%20hot%20and%20humid%20afternoon%20in%20late%20September%20this%20year%2C%20I%20spoke%20to%20electrician%20Raj%20Kishore%2C%20who%20was%20replacing%20an%20old%20meter%20that%20had%20stopped%20giving%20the%20%E2%80%9Cmeter%20reading%E2%80%9D%20for%20Tata%20Power%20Delhi%20Distribution%20Limited.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20joint%20venture%20between%20Tata%20Power%20and%20the%20Delhi%20government%2C%20with%20the%20majority%20stake%20with%20the%20Tatas%2C%20supplies%20power%20to%20North%20and%20north-west%20Delhi%2C%20serving%201.9%20million%20customers.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EKishore%20switched%20off%20the%20electricity%20supply%20of%20the%20building%2C%20lowered%20the%20visor%20of%20his%20helmet%20and%20started%20working.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20told%20me%20he%20graduated%20from%20an%20Industrial%20Training%20Institute%20or%20ITI%20in%202010%2C%20and%20earned%20Rs%2020%2C000%20a%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20he%20is%20employed%20through%20a%20contractor%20by%20the%20Tatas.%20The%20contractor%20deducts%20provident%20fund%20and%20Employee%20State%20Insurance%2C%20or%20ESI%2C%20which%20allows%20him%20to%20access%20certain%20government-run%20medical%20facilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EKishore%20said%20that%20any%20accident%20on%20the%20job%2C%20the%20likelihood%20of%20which%20is%20high%20in%20his%20line%20of%20work%2C%20will%20not%20be%20met%20with%20any%20monetary%20compensation.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20risk%20is%20all%20mine%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%2C%20before%20requesting%20that%20I%20do%20not%20talk%20to%20him%20while%20he%20is%20working.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20insurance%20that%20Kishore%E2%80%99s%20contractor%2C%20and%20others%2C%20subscribe%20to%20allows%20three%20days%20of%20accident%20leave%20where%20he%20can%20draw%2090%25%20of%20his%20daily%20wages%20%E2%80%93%20a%20pitiful%20amount.%20Any%20further%20assistance%20will%20involve%20a%20labour%20tribunal.%20Contractors%20cheating%20skilled%20workers%20by%20deducting%20the%20employer%E2%80%99s%20share%20of%20ESI%20also%20from%20the%20worker%E2%80%99s%20salary%20is%20not%20an%20uncommon%20story.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20467px)%2085vw%2C%20467px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F20115230%2Fimage-1414.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22467%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F20115230%2Fimage-1414.png%20536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F20115230%2Fimage-1414-223x300.png%20223w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-680963%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22629%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ERaj%20Kishore%20adjusts%20his%20visor%20as%20he%20replaces%20a%20meter%20for%20Tata%20Power%20Delhi%20Dustribution%20Limited.%20He%20is%20employed%20by%20the%20company%20through%20a%20contractor.%20Contracted%20jobs%20are%20insecure%20and%20pay%20low%20wages%20with%20minimal%20benefits.%20Photo%20provided%20by%20author.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EKishore%20stays%20in%20a%20rented%20accommodation%20with%20his%20wife%2C%20children%2C%20and%20parents.%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EGuzara%20mushkil%20se%20hota%20hai%3C%2Fem%3E%20(it%20is%20tough%20to%20make%20two%20ends%20meet)%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAn%20Indian%20Institute%20of%20Technology%20or%20IIT%20graduate%20of%202010%20would%2C%20in%20contrast%2C%20earn%20a%20few%20crores%20annually.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWages%20of%20skilled%20workers%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20private%20sector%20remain%20so%20depressed%2C%20benefits%20so%20dismal%20and%20jobs%20so%20precarious%2C%20that%20it%20makes%20a%20majority%20hanker%20for%20government%20jobs.%20They%20sit%20for%20one%20exam%20after%20another%2C%20and%20demand%20accountability%20from%20a%20system%20which%20resists%20all%20these%20efforts.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20desire%20to%20have%20government%20jobs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EReeta%20Mahto%2C%20after%20graduating%20from%20a%20government-run%20ITI%20in%20Kanpur%2C%20completed%20her%20one-year%20apprenticeship%20in%20the%20Indian%20Railways%20in%202018-19.%20She%20earned%20a%20monthly%20stipend%20of%20Rs%205%2C800.%20The%20Indian%20Railways%20stopped%20absorbing%20apprentices%20automatically%2C%20which%20it%20used%20to%20do%20earlier.%20Apprentices%20need%20to%20sit%20for%20an%20exam%20%E2%80%93%20most%20probably%20to%20reduce%20the%20numbers.%20Mahto%20could%20not%20make%20the%20cut.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShe%20was%20disappointed%2C%20and%20said%20apprentices%20are%20agitating%20all%20over%20the%20country%20to%20get%20jobs%20in%20the%20Railways.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBhupendra%20Thakur%2C%20who%20graduated%20from%20an%20ITI%20as%20an%20electrician%2C%20is%20protesting%20too.%20He%20sat%20for%20an%20exam%20after%20graduating%20and%20enrolled%20in%20an%20additional%20course%20which%20allowed%20him%20to%20teach%20in%20ITIs%2C%20but%20the%20Rajasthan%20government%20is%20not%20filling%20vacancies.%20Thakur%20is%20part%20of%20the%20protests%20to%20pressurise%20the%20Gehlot%20government%2C%20which%20faces%20an%20election%20in%20a%20few%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20desire%20for%20government%20jobs%20makes%20sensational%20front-page%20headlines%20in%20the%20shape%20of%20%E2%80%9Clakhs%20apply%20for%20peon%20vacancy%E2%80%9D%20but%20Indian%20media%20has%20never%20interrogated%20why%20people%20want%20these%20jobs.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20not%20surprising%20that%20so%20many%20people%20are%20queuing%20for%20regular%20government%20jobs.%20These%20are%20the%20only%20jobs%20that%20are%20not%20only%20reasonably%20well-paid%20but%20also%20secure.%20A%20regular%20government%20job%20means%20lifetime%20security%20(including%20pension)%20at%20a%20reasonably%20comfortable%20level%2C%20at%20least%20compared%20with%20most%20alternatives.%20No%20wonder%20these%20jobs%20are%20in%20such%20high%20demand.%20By%20extension%2C%20there%20is%20a%20high%20demand%20even%20for%20contractual%20government%20jobs%2C%20since%20a%20contractual%20job%20is%20always%20a%20potential%20springboard%20to%20a%20regular%20job%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20economist%20and%20activist%20Jean%20Dreze.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20am%20not%20sure%20whether%20India%20is%20unique%20in%20this%20respect%2C%20but%20it%20is%20almost%20certainly%20unusual%20in%20the%20extent%20of%20the%20salary%20and%20pension%20gap%20between%20regular%20government%20jobs%20and%20the%20private%20sector%2C%20as%20well%20as%20in%20the%20extent%20of%20job%20security%20in%20the%20public%20sector%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Dreze.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESkill%20India%20will%20not%20succeed%20as%20long%20as%20it%20fails%20to%20reign%20in%20Corporate%20India%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Ccasualisation%E2%80%9D%2C%20and%20their%20lack%20of%20will%20to%20pay%20a%20comfortable%20salary%20to%20its%20own%20workers.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAn%20ignored%20report%20card%20and%20the%20transfer%20of%20an%20official%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20skills%20programme%20has%20left%20out%20another%20gap%3A%20its%20backbone%2C%20the%20Industrial%20Training%20Institutes.%20Fifteen%20thousand%20ITIs%2C%20of%20which%2022%25%20are%20government-owned%2C%20form%20the%20public%20infrastructure%20of%20skills%20built%20with%20taxpayer%20money.%20This%20has%20been%20allowed%20to%20die.%20An%20excellent%20and%20in-depth%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.niti.gov.in%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2F2023-02%2FITI_Report_02022023.pdf%5C%22%3ENITI%20Aayog%20report%20in%20January%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%20laid%20out%20the%20symptoms%20and%20medicines%20for%20the%20comatose%20patient%20in%2098%20pages.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20titled%20%E2%80%98Transforming%20Industrial%20Training%20Institutes%E2%80%99%20actually%20had%20people%20visit%20ITIs%2C%20talk%20to%20working%20class%20enrolled%20in%20them%2C%20and%20even%20analyse%20their%20budgets.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20found%20seat%20occupancy%20in%20government%20ITIs%20at%2057%25%20higher%20than%20in%20private%20ITIs%20where%20only%2043%25%20of%20the%20seats%2C%20i.e.%2C%20less%20than%20half%2C%20are%20occupied.%20Placements%20as%20well%20as%20work%20conditions%20of%20ITI%20graduates%20are%20areas%20of%20concern.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20an%20annual%20public%20expenditure%20of%20about%20Rs%2010%2C000%20crore%20in%20running%20the%20ecosystem%20of%203%2C500%20government%20ITIs%2C%20besides%20the%20Rs%202%2C200%20crore%20STRIVE%20scheme%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EKundan%20Kumar%2C%20an%20IAS%20officer%20and%20advisor%20for%20Skill%20Development%20and%20Employment%20vertical%20at%20NITI%20Aayog%2C%20who%20wrote%20the%20report%E2%80%99s%20preface%2C%20was%20transferred%20out%2C%20despite%20having%20an%20eight-year%20term%20at%20the%20think%20tank%20in%202021.%20When%20I%20tracked%20Kumar%20down%20to%20his%20new%20post%20in%20Bihar%20Bhawan%2C%20he%20refused%20to%20comment%20on%20the%20report%2C%20or%20anything%20else%20on%20this%20subject.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20reports%2C%20it%20seems%2C%20will%20languish%20in%20the%20Skill%20India%20bog.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Faparna-kalra%5C%22%3EAparna%20Kalra%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0is%20a%20Delhi%20School%20of%20Economics%20alumnus%20whose%20forte%20is%20investigations%2C%20profiles%20and%20data%20journalism.%20She%20has%20worked%20as%20a%20fact-checker%20on%20a%20Facebook%20project%20for%20AFP.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697787042000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F19165415%2Fimage-1409.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flabour%2Fwhy-i-cant-find-a-good-plumber-exploring-the-skill-india-mess%22%2C