aine-and-israel-hamas-wars-12988076%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BIf%20Girl%20Gives%20In%20To%20Pleasure%20Of%202%20Minutes%2C%20She%20Is...%26quot%3B%3A%20Calcutta%20High%20Court%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EHearing%20a%20teenager's%20request%20against%20his%20conviction%20in%20a%20rape%20case%2C%20Calcutta%20High%20Court%20issued%20a%20list%20of%20guidelines%20for%20adolescent%20boys%20and%20girls%20asking%20them%20to%20control%20their%20sexual%20urges%20and%20also%20respect%20the%20dignity%20and%20bodily%20autonomy%20of%20the%20other%20gender.%20The%20teenager%20last%20year%20was%20sentenced%20to%2020%20years%20in%20prison%20by%20a%20sessions%20court%20for%20having%20sex%20with%20his%20romantic%20partner%2C%20who%20is%20a%20minor.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20hearing%2C%20the%20girl%20had%20told%20the%20court%20that%20she%20was%20in%20a%20relationship%20of%20her%20own%20will%20and%20had%20subsequently%20married%20him.%20She%20said%20that%20the%20age%20of%20consent%20for%20sex%20in%20India%20is%2018%20and%20their%20relationship%20was%20an%20offense.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EConsent%20given%20by%20a%20person%20aged%20below%2018%20is%20not%20regarded%20as%20valid%20and%20sexual%20intercourse%20with%20them%20amounts%20to%20rape%20under%20the%20Protection%20of%20Children%20from%20Sexual%20Offences%20Act%20(POCSO).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20two-judge%20bench%20of%20Justices%20Chitta%20Ranjan%20Dash%20and%20Partha%20Sarathi%20Sen%20set%20aside%20the%20verdict%20of%20the%20sessions%20court%20and%20called%20for%20comprehensive%20sex%20education%20in%20schools%20to%20avoid%20legal%20complications%20arising%20from%20sexual%20relations%20at%20a%20young%20age.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20said%20that%20sex%20among%20adolescents%20is%20normal%20but%20arousal%20of%20such%20urge%20is%20dependent%20on%20action%20by%20the%20individual%2C%20maybe%20a%20man%20or%20woman.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20urged%20girls%20to%20control%20their%20sexual%20urges%20and%20not%20gi