s%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-africa-67155786.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Canada%20withdraws%2041%20diplomats%20from%20India%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697767051000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F101CC%2Fproduction%2F_131469956_b86bfdb34d5ef12e9af8e06f664307b8290993360_11_6720_37811000x563.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-us-canada-67162218%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22It%20is%20the%20latest%20in%20a%20row%20between%20the%20two%20nations%20over%20the%20murder%20of%20a%20Sikh%20separatist%20leader%20on%20Canadian%20soil.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A354%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-us-canada-67162218%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-us-canada-67162218.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-us-canada-67162218.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Christ's%20photo%20at%20home%20doesn't%20mean%20person%20has%20converted'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697766682000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-104567988%2Cimgsize-643868.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fnagpur%2Fjesus-christs-photo-at-home-doesnt-mean-person-has-converted-bombay-high-court%2Farticleshow%2F104567962.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Nagpur%20bench%20of%20the%20Bombay%20high%20court%20has%20ruled%20that%20having%20a%20photograph%20of%20a%20religious%20figure%20at%20home%20does%20not%20mean%20a%20person%20is%20professing%20that%20religion.%20The%20decision%20was%20made%20in%20response%20to%20a%20plea%20by%20a%2017-year-old%20girl%20whose%20caste%20validity%20claim%20was%20denied%20because%20a%20vigilance%20officer%20found%20a%20photo%20of%20Jesus%20Christ%20at%20her%20home.%20The%20court%20stated%20that%20the%20presence%20of%20the%20photograph%20did%20not%20indicate%20a%20conversion%20to%20Christianity%20and%20ordered%20the%20quashing%20of%20the%20caste%20claim%20denial.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22VAIBHAV%20GANJAPURE%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fnagpur%2Fjesus-christs-photo-at-home-doesnt-mean-person-has-converted-bombay-high-court%2Farticleshow%2F104567962.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20Real%20Solution%20to%20Cauvery%20River%20Dispute%20Lies%20in%20Effective%20Water%20Conservation%20Strategy%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F19161301%2FThe-Wire-44-1.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Cauvery%20River%2C%20which%20flows%20through%20the%20southern%20Indian%20states%20of%20Kerala%2C%20Karnataka%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20and%20the%20Union%20territory%20of%20Puducherry%2C%20has%20been%20a%20source%20of%20persistent%20and%20intricate%20water%20conflict.%20The%20dispute%20between%20Karnataka%20and%20Tamil%20Nadu%20over%20the%20Cauvery%20River%20is%20traced%20back%20to%20as%20early%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.researchgate.net%2Fpublication%2F339184358_Strategic_Insights_into_the_Cauvery_River_Dispute_in_India%5C%22%3E1890%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20with%20roots%20in%20the%20pre-independence%20era%20when%20the%20then%20princely%20states%20of%20Mysore%20(now%20Karnataka)%20and%20Madras%20(now%20Tamil%20Nadu)%20contended%20for%20control%20over%20the%20river%E2%80%99s%20waters.%20Even%20after%20independence%2C%20the%20issue%20has%20persisted%2C%20revolving%20around%20the%20judicious%20sharing%20and%20utilisation%20of%20water%20resources%2C%20and%20has%20resulted%20in%20numerous%20legal%20battles%2C%20protests%2C%20and%20political%20maneuvering.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20tussle%20between%20the%20lower%20riparian%20state%20of%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20with%20a%20share%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmain.sci.gov.in%2Fsupremecourt%2F2007%2F11993%2F11993_2007_Judgement_16-Feb-2018.pdf%5C%22%3E404.25%20tmc%20(thousand%20million%20cubic%20feet)%3C%2Fa%3E%20annually%2C%20and%20the%20upper%20riparian%20state%20of%20Karnataka%2C%20which%20has%20a%20share%20of%20284.75%20tmc%2C%20has%20aggravated%20today%20due%20to%20the%20failure%20of%20southwest%20monsoons%20in%20Karnataka%20this%20season.%20Judicial%20and%20quasi-judicial%20bodies%20formed%20to%20resolve%20the%20issues%20over%20the%20years%20have%20failed.%20Despite%20these%20efforts%2C%20a%20lasting%20resolution%20still%20needs%20to%20be%20achieved%2C%20with%20both%20states%20continually%20vying%20for%20their%20rightful%20share%20of%20the%20river%E2%80%99s%20water.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20article%20focuses%20on%20the%20key%20findings%20from%20research%20that%20must%20guide%20the%20dispute%20resolution%20mechanisms.%20It%20is%20high%20time%20to%20advocate%20not%20for%20the%20rightful%20share%20of%20water%20for%20each%20state%20but%20the%20reasonable%20share%20in%20water%20conservation%20mechanisms%20by%20both%20states%20given%20the%20climate%20crises.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fcauvery-bengaluru-mettur-krishnarajasagar%5C%22%3ESoon%2C%20We%20May%20Not%20Have%20a%20Cauvery%20River%20to%20Fight%20Over%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20Nobel%20Laureate%20Ronald%20Coase%2C%20if%20there%20are%20low%20transaction%20costs%20and%20clear%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.econ.iastate.edu%2Fclasses%2Ftsc220%2Fhallam%2FCoase.pdf%5C%22%3Eproperty%20rights%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20two%20states%20could%20engage%20in%20voluntary%20negotiations%20to%20efficiently%20allocate%20the%20river%20water.%20However%2C%20the%20historical%20complexities%20of%20the%20dispute%2C%20high%20transaction%20costs%2C%20and%20political%20factors%20do%20not%20allow%20efficient%20bargaining.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.garretthardinsociety.org%2Farticles%2Fart_tragedy_of_the_commons.html%5C%22%3ETragedy%20of%20the%20Commons%3C%2Fa%3E%20perspective%20comes%20into%20play%2C%20highlighting%20the%20risk%20of%20overuse%20and%20depletion%20of%20the%20Cauvery%20River%20as%20a%20common-pool%20resource%20without%20adequate%20regulation%20or%20property%20rights.%20This%20perspective%20underscores%20the%20need%20for%20government%20intervention%20and%20regulatory%20mechanisms%20to%20prevent%20the%20Tragedy%2C%20acknowledging%20the%20collective%20action%20problem%20where%20individual%20interests%20can%20lead%20to%20suboptimal%20outcomes%20for%20both%20the%20states%20and%20the%20environment.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20transboundary%20water%20disputes%2C%20upstream%20states%20typically%20apply%20the%20Harmon%20doctrine%20(source-based%20water%20rights).%20In%20contrast%2C%20downstream%20states%20adhere%20to%20historical%20principles%20(prioritising%20primary%20water%20rights%20for%20historical%20users)%20as%20per%20a%20study%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.researchgate.net%2Fpublication%2F328381178_Conflict_over_Cauvery_Waters_Imperatives_for_Innovative_Policy_Options%5C%22%3Ethe%20Observer%20Research%20Foundation%20(2018)%3C%2Fa%3E.%20International%20guidelines%20can%20advocate%20for%20equitable%20and%20reasonable%20utilisation%20of%20transboundary%20waters%20and%20offer%20valuable%20insights%20into%20the%20resolution%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20judgement%20in%202018%20on%20Karnataka%E2%80%99s%20appeal%20discusses%20the%20water-sharing%20formula%20in%20the%20Cauvery%20basin%20and%20references%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmain.sci.gov.in%2Fsupremecourt%2F2007%2F11993%2F11993_2007_Judgement_16-Feb-2018.pdf%5C%22%3Ethe%20Helsinki%2C%20Berlin%2C%20and%20Compoine%20rules%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Water%20allocation%20to%20each%20party%20state%20is%20based%20on%20the%20total%20available%20yield%20generated%20in%20the%20Cauvery%20basin.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20judgement%2C%20the%20full%20yield%20figure%20of%20the%20Cauvery%20basin%20areas%20within%20the%20states%20of%20Karnataka%2C%20Kerala%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20and%20the%20Union%20territory%20of%20Pondicherry%20was%20estimated%20at%20740%20tmc%2C%20assuming%2050%25%20dependability.%20Of%20the%20740%20tmc%2C%2014%20tmc%20is%20apportioned%20for%20environmental%20protection%20and%20inevitable%20flows%20to%20the%20sea%2C%20leaving%20around%20726%20tmc%20of%20water%20shared%20among%20the%20four%20riparians.%20The%20judgment%20mentions%20that%20the%20Cauvery%20basin%E2%80%99s%20rainfall%2C%20flows%2C%20and%20crop%20pattern%20will%20determine%20water%20release%20during%20a%20year%20of%20distress.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F02%2F16201207%2Ffile-Cauvery.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Rally%20for%20Rivers%2C%20Cauvery%20Calling%2C%20Isha%20Foundation%2C%20Jaggi%20Vasudev%2C%20tree%20plantation%2C%20Cauvery%20river%2C%20sand%20mining%2C%20groundwater%20extraction%2C%20Medha%20Patkar%2C%20Sardar%20Sarovar%20Dam%2C%20Narmada%20Bachao%20Andolan%2C%20Mekedatu%20dam%2C%20Swachh%20Bharat%2C%20Harangi%2C%20Kabini%2C%20Shimsha%2C%20Hemavati%2C%20Arkavathi%2C%20Suvarnavathi%2C%20Lakshmana%20Thirtha%2C%20Lokapavani%2C%20Bhavani%2C%20Noyyal%2C%20Amaravati%2C%20Amazon%20rainforest%2C%20Cauvery%20basin%2C%20grasslands%2C%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%222100%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-224984%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221444%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EA%20view%20of%20the%20Cauvery%20River.%20Photo%3A%20File%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20water-sharing%20formula%20is%20essential%2C%20it%20should%20integrate%20a%20water%20conservation%20strategy%2C%20reflecting%20the%20shared%20responsibility%20of%20the%20states%20towards%20Cauvery%20as%20a%20property.%20Investments%20in%20irrigation%20efficiency%2C%20diversion%20of%20the%20cropping%20pattern%2C%20water%20conservation%2C%20or%20any%20measures%20to%20regulate%20the%20demand%20for%20water%20from%20both%20states%20need%20emphasis%20during%20water%20sharing.%20These%20factors%20become%20relevant%20when%20the%20water%20supply%20is%20constrained%2C%20and%20shortages%20are%20recurrent%20over%20the%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFirstly%2C%20the%20actual%20cost%20of%20irrigation%20water%20becomes%20inconsequential%2C%20making%20agricultural%20water%20almost%20a%20free%20resource%20in%20the%20basin.%20The%20free%20resource%20has%20resulted%20in%20inefficient%20demand-side%20management%20of%20irrigation%20water%20as%20farmers%20in%20other%20irrigation%20command%20areas%20habitually%20utilise%20large%20amounts%20of%20water%20from%20the%20river%20for%20a%20longer%20time%20with%20low%20end-use%20efficiency.%20Conserving%20scarce%20resources%20must%20take%20precedence%20over%20subsidising%20agriculture%20for%20redistributive%20justice%20during%20crises.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESecondly%2C%20diversifying%20crop%20patterns%20in%20the%20Cauvery%20Delta%2C%20in%20both%20states%2C%20forms%20a%20solution%20for%20managing%20demand%20for%20irrigation.%20A%20sudden%20shift%20from%20high-value%20crops%20to%20other%20crops%20may%20be%20challenging%2C%20but%20promoting%20crop%20diversification%20through%20a%20minimum%20support%20price%20regime%20favoring%20drier%20crops%2C%20millets%2C%20horticulture%2C%20and%20oilseeds%20(which%20are%20suited%20to%20both%20States%20geographical%20conditions)%20to%20nudge%20farmers%20promotes%20less%20water-intensive%20crops%20in%20both%20States.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fwho-is-willing-to-find-a-long-term-solution-to-the-cauvery-dispute%5C%22%3EWho%20Is%20Willing%20to%20Find%20a%20Long-Term%20Solution%20to%20the%20Cauvery%20Dispute%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThirdly%2C%20water%20conservation%20is%20neglected%20by%20the%20states%20because%2C%20Bengaluru%2C%20which%20depends%20on%20Cauvery%20for%20its%20water%20needs%2C%20ranks%20second%20among%20Indian%20metros%20in%20water%20wastage%20as%20per%20an%20article%20in%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fbengaluru-ranks-second-in-water-wastage%23%3A~%3Atext%3DBengaluru%25E2%2580%2599s%2520water%2520loss%2520is%2520the%2520second%2520highest%2520among%2Cpegged%2520Bengaluru%25E2%2580%2599s%2520losses%2520at%252048%2525%2520three%2520years%2520ago.%5C%22%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E.%20In%20addition%2C%20it%20is%20ironic%20to%20note%20that%20Tamil%20Nadu%20received%20a%20%24100%20million%20loan%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.adb.org%2Fnews%2Fadb-loan-help-tackle-water-stress-climate-threats-india-s-cauvery-delta%5C%22%3Ethe%20Asian%20Development%20Bank%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20reduce%20water%20stress%20in%20the%20Cauvery%20Delta%20in%202016%20and%20the%20projected%20completion%20in%202020%2C%20yet%20the%20water%20demand%20persists.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20water%20pollution%20in%20the%20Cauvery%20Basin%20is%20an%20overlooked%20dimension.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Facr.iitm.ac.in%2Fiitm_in_news%2Fiit-madras-researchers-find-high-levels-of-pharmaceutical-contaminants-in-the-river-cauvery%2F%5C%22%3EAs%20per%20a%20study%20by%20IIT%20Madras%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20Cauvery%20water%20is%20plagued%20by%20pharmaceutical%20contaminants.%20Adding%20to%20it%2C%20the%20industrial%20effluents%2C%20untreated%20sewage%2C%20and%20agricultural%20runoff%20have%20severely%20compromised%20the%20quality%20of%20the%20Cauvery%E2%80%99s%20waters.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHence%2C%20water%20demand%20management%20and%20conservation%20are%20pivotal%20in%20resolving%20the%20Cauvery%20dispute.%20Prioritising%20the%20preservation%20of%20catchment%20areas%20and%20river%20basins%20to%20ensure%20a%20sustainable%20water%20supply%20for%20both%20states.%20The%20politicisation%20of%20water%20resources%20has%20exacerbated%20the%20Cauvery%20dispute%2C%20and%20shifting%20the%20focus%20from%20water%20sharing%20to%20water%20conservation%20is%20imperative%20for%20the%20water-sharing%20formula%2C%20given%20the%20long-time%20and%20recurrent%20battle%20between%20the%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2Fpolitics-california-colorado-river-climate-and-environment-d9f1c7c0dbb1633ae74782d23ea9b78a%5C%22%3ECalifornia%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20instance%2C%20implemented%20a%2015-year%20plan%20to%20reduce%20its%20reliance%20on%20Colorado%20River%20water%2C%20emphasising%20water%20conservation%2C%20recycling%2C%20and%20storage%20as%20part%20of%20its%20separation%20from%20an%20overreliance%20on%20the%20river.%20Currently%2C%20the%20seven%20states%20involved%20in%20Colorado%20River%20water%20sharing%20are%20considering%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2Fpolitics-california-colorado-river-climate-and-environment-d9f1c7c0dbb1633ae74782d23ea9b78a%5C%22%3Ehow%20to%20cut%20the%20demand%20for%20water%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Hence%2C%20the%20Cauvery%20water%20dispute%20is%20far%20more%20intricate%20considering%20the%20water%20conservation%20than%20a%20mere%20dispute%20between%20the%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETo%20move%20forward%2C%20stakeholders%20must%20recognise%20the%20urgent%20need%20for%20a%20new%20narrative%20that%20prioritises%20the%20sustainable%20use%20of%20water%20resources%2C%20minimises%20ecological%20harm%2C%20and%20embraces%20the%20challenges%20posed%20by%20climate%20change.%20Legal%20requirements%20advocating%20for%20water%20conservation%20and%20demand%20management%2C%20as%20a%20prerequisite%20for%20water%20sharing%20rights%2C%20is%20the%20only%20lasting%20solution%20to%20the%20age-old%20conflict.%20Consequently%2C%20Cauvery%20River%20remains%20a%20lifeline%20for%20both%20Karnataka%20and%20Tamil%20Nadu%20in%20the%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ERoopa%20Patavardhan%2C%20Faculty%20at%20Department%20of%20Economics%20Christ%20University%2C%20Bengaluru.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697765443000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F19161301%2FThe-Wire-44-1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fthe-real-solution-to-cauvery-river-dispute-lies-in-effective-water-conservation-strategy%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20politicisation%20of%20water%20resources%20has%20made%20it%20a%20recurring%20dispute%20between%20Tamil%20Nadu%20and%20Karnataka.%20Shifting%20the%20focus%20from%20water%20sharing%20to%20water%20conservation%20will%20help%20both%20sides%20arrive%20at%20an%20acceptable%20water-sharing%20formula.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fthe-real-solution-to-cauvery-river-dispute-lies-in-effective-water-conservation-strategy%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Kashmiri%20Reporter's%20Award%20Cancelled%20as%20Her%20Views%20Weren't%20Aligned%20With%20Government%2C%20Says%20Pune%20Institute%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F19230819%2FSafina-Nabi.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Two%20days%20after%20the%20Pune-based%20private%20institute%20MIT-WPU%20withdrew%20a%20journalism%20award%20that%20had%20already%20been%20announced%20for%20Kashmiri%20reporter%20Safina%20Nabi%2C%20the%20organisers%20have%20said%20they%20took%20their%20decision%20because%20her%20views%20could%20potentially%20be%20seen%20as%C2%A0%20%E2%80%9Ccontentious%E2%80%9D%20and%20not%20aligned%20with%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20foreign%20policy%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENabi%E2%80%99s%20report%2C%20%E2%80%98%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscroll.in%2Farticle%2F1015849%2Fhow-kashmirs-half-widows-are-denied-their-basic-property-rights%5C%22%3EThe%20half%20widows%20of%20Kashmir%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%99%2C%20was%20chosen%20as%20the%20winner%20in%20the%20category%20of%20%E2%80%98journalism%20that%20promoted%20empathy%2C%20understanding%20and%20inclusivity%20in%20society%E2%80%99%20by%20a%20jury%20comprising%20three%20members%20from%20the%20institute%20and%20four%20external%20members.%20As%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fpune-institute-cancels-award-for-kashmiri-journalist-jury-refuses-to-attend-event-in-protest%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20first%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Nabi%20was%20officially%20informed%20about%20the%20award%20and%20sent%20a%20plane%20ticket%20so%20she%20could%20travel%20to%20Pune%20to%20receive%20it%20on%20October%2018%2C%20only%20to%20be%20told%20on%20October%2016%20that%20her%20award%20had%20been%20cancelled%20and%20that%20she%20should%20not%20make%20the%20journey.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENabi%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20she%20was%20informed%20by%20the%20organisers%20by%20telephone%20that%20the%20award%20was%20cancelled%20by%20the%20university%E2%80%99s%20management%20in%20the%20face%20of%20right-wing%20political%20pressure.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20cancellation%20led%20to%20the%20three%20independent%20jury%20members%20boycotting%20the%20award%20function.%20One%20of%20the%20members%2C%20M.K.%20Venu%2C%20a%20founding%20editor%20of%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20said%20that%20the%20institute%20management%E2%80%99s%20decision%20to%20drop%20Nabi%20came%20as%20a%20shock%20to%20them.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20discussed%20amongst%20ourselves%20and%20decided%20that%20the%20best%20statement%20to%20make%20would%20be%20to%20not%20attend%20the%20event%E2%80%A6%20Kashmiri%20journalists%20are%20being%20subjected%20to%20an%20altogether%20different%20level%20of%20censorship%20and%20harassment%20which%20is%20totally%20unconscionable.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20institute%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmitwpu.edu.in%2Fprogrammes%2Fschool-of-liberal-arts-humanities%2Fdepartment-of-media-and-communication%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewhich%20offers%20a%20BA%20and%20MA%20in%20media%20and%20communication%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20initially%20chose%20not%20to%20respond%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%98s%20request%20for%20a%20comment%20but%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Fcities%2Fpune-news%2Fkashmiri-reporter-denied-award-last-minute-by-mitwpu-101697653090895.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esubsequently%20told%20other%20news%20platforms%20which%20followed%20up%20on%20the%20story%20%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20an%20%E2%80%9Cinternal%20miscommunication%E2%80%9D%20had%20led%20to%20the%20%E2%80%9Cunfortunate%20situation%E2%80%9D.%20It%20said%20that%20it%20respected%20Nabi%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Clarger%20work%20in%20the%20field%E2%80%9D%20and%20would%20be%20honouring%20her%20in%20a%20%E2%80%9Cforthcoming%20bigger%20award%20ceremony%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20news%20agency%20PTI%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mid-day.com%2Fnews%2Findia-news%2Farticle%2Fpune-institute-backtracks-on-honouring-kashmiri-journalist-following-political-pressure-23315287%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Thursday%20that%20the%20institute%20administration%20had%20said%20a%20%E2%80%9Ccommunication%20gap%E2%80%9D%20led%20to%20the%20cancellation%20and%20that%20Nabi%20would%20be%20invited%20to%20another%20event%2C%20the%20%E2%80%98Bhartiya%20Chhatra%20Sansad%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20Thursday%20evening%2C%20the%20MIT-WPU%20finally%20sent%20a%20statement%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%20%3C%2Fem%3Ein%20which%20an%20entirely%20different%20explanation%20for%20the%20canceled%20award%20was%20proffered.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAcknowledging%20that%20the%20jury%20had%20indeed%20chosen%20Nabi%20as%20the%20award%E2%80%99s%20recipient%2C%20the%20institute%20said%20that%20it%20was%20%E2%80%9Cmade%20aware%20of%20some%20of%20her%20published%20opinions%20and%20views%2C%20which%20have%20the%20potential%20to%20be%20viewed%20as%20contentious%20and%20not%20in%20alignment%20with%20the%20foreign%20policy%20of%20the%20Indian%20government.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20statement%20gave%20no%20details%20of%20what%20these%20opinions%20and%20views%20were%20or%20why%20a%20journalism%20school%20expects%20reporters%20to%20align%20themselves%20with%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20policies.%20And%20while%20claiming%20that%20there%20had%20been%20no%20external%20pressure%2C%20the%20institute%20left%20unexplained%20how%20it%20had%20suddenly%20been%20%E2%80%9Cmade%20aware%E2%80%9D%20of%20Nabi%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Copinions%20and%20views%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWithout%20taking%20a%20stance%20of%20either%20endorsing%20or%20renouncing%20her%20expressed%20views%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9Cwe%20anticipated%20that%20presenting%20her%20with%20an%20award%20at%20this%20time%20could%20have%20given%20rise%20to%20unwelcome%20controversies.%20Such%20controversies%20are%20something%20our%20institution%2C%20being%20an%20academic%2C%20apolitical%2C%20and%20non-partisan%20entity%2C%20should%20not%20be%20associated%20with%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMIT-WPU%20denied%20any%20%E2%80%9Cexternal%20political%20or%20non-political%20pressure%E2%80%9D%20to%20rescind%20the%20award%20granted%20to%20Nabi.%20%E2%80%9C%E2%80%A6our%20decision%20should%20be%20understood%20as%20an%20effort%20to%20safeguard%20the%20fundamental%20purpose%20of%20the%20conference%20and%20maintain%20the%20unshakable%20academic%20integrity%20of%20our%20institution%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20statement%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Grim%20indicator%20of%20new%20normal%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%20%3C%2Fem%3Eabout%20the%20MIT-WPU%20statement%2C%C2%A0%20Nabi%20slammed%20the%20institute%20for%20its%20%E2%80%9Cneedless%20cover-ups%E2%80%9D%2C%20adding%20that%20she%20will%20not%20attend%20any%20event%20that%20it%20holds%20in%20the%20future.%20%E2%80%9CDon%E2%80%99t%20call%20this%20mess%20an%20internal%20discord%2C%20and%20above%20all%20I%20am%20far%20from%20publishing%20anything%20contentious.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Kashmiri%20journalist%2C%20who%20has%20been%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsafinanabi.contently.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epublished%20widely%20in%20India%20and%20abroad%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20said%20that%20the%20past%20few%20days%20%E2%80%9Chave%20been%20shocking%20and%20a%20grim%20indicator%20of%20the%20new%20normal%E2%80%9D%2C%20but%20that%20she%20appreciated%20the%20jury%E2%80%99s%20decision%20to%20boycott%20the%20event%20in%20protest.%20This%20had%20helped%20%E2%80%9Creaffirm%20my%20faith%20and%20show%20me%20that%20journalism%20is%20in%20safe%20hands.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENabi%20said%20that%20the%20primary%20focus%20of%20her%20work%20has%20revolved%20around%20women%2C%20%E2%80%9Cespecially%20the%20women%20of%20my%20country%2C%20and%20contributing%20towards%20their%20advancement%20and%20empowerment.%E2%80%9D%20For%20years%20now%2C%20she%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20strived%20to%20be%20the%20storyteller%20documenting%20tales%20of%20perseverance%20and%20injustice.%20I%20do%20not%20wish%20to%20change%20that%20now%20and%20be%20the%20story%20itself.%20I%20am%20deeply%20appreciative%20of%20all%20the%20support%20I%20have%20received%20in%20the%20past%20few%20days.%20The%20fight%20for%20honest%20storytelling%20will%20continue.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWithdrawal%20of%20award%20%E2%80%98disgusting%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESenior%20journalist%20Gurbir%20Singh%2C%20who%20heads%20the%20Mumbai%20Press%20Club%20which%20hands%20out%20the%20prestigious%20Red%20Ink%20Awards%20for%20journalism%20every%20year%2C%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%20%3C%2Fem%3Ethat%20the%20withdrawal%20of%20the%20award%20given%20to%20Nabi%20is%20%E2%80%9Cdisgusting%20and%20deserves%20to%20be%20condemned%20in%20the%20strongest%20possible%20terms%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CShe%20had%20won%20the%20award%20in%20a%20merit-based%20selection%20by%20an%20independent%20jury.%20The%20action%20by%20the%20institute%20is%20penalising%20Nabi%20for%20her%20Kashmiriyat%20and%20for%20highlighting%20a%20human%20tragedy%20in%20the%20state.%20Is%20this%20%E2%80%98nationalism%E2%80%99%2C%20aimed%20at%20integrating%20the%20country%2C%20or%20xenophobic%20discrimination%20dividing%20our%20country%20further%3F%20As%20journalists%2C%20we%20should%20think%20of%20how%20to%20undo%20this%20wrong%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Network%20of%20Women%20in%20Media%2C%20India%20has%20written%20to%20MIT-WPU%20to%20condemn%20the%20institute%E2%80%99s%20decision.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FNWM_India%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40NWM_India%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20written%20to%20the%20Maharashtra%20Institute%20of%20Technology-World%20Peace%20University%2C%20and%20registered%20its%20condemnation%20of%20the%20cancellation%20of%20the%20award%20to%20Safina%20Nabi.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsoul_restlesss%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40soul_restlesss%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%F0%9F%94%97%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2Fy4QnvjT0xT%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2Fy4QnvjT0xT%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F1xgjJs6WQO%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2F1xgjJs6WQO%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20NWMIndia%20(%40NWM_India)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FNWM_India%2Fstatus%2F1715250773502914912%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EOctober%2020%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COrdinarily%2C%20the%20award%20would%20have%20signalled%20your%20institution%E2%80%99s%20recognition%20of%20the%20critical%20importance%20of%20storytelling%20in%20areas%20of%20intense%20conflict.%20To%20withdraw%20from