nd%20then%20later%20on%20in%20the%20Vietnam%20War.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Vietnam%2C%20the%20Vietcong%20forces%20built%20a%20huge%20network%20of%20tunnels%20%E2%80%94%20used%20as%20supply%20routes%2C%20to%20store%20ammunition%2C%20and%20to%20house%20infrastructure%20like%20hospitals%20%E2%80%94%20the%20largest%20among%20them%20being%20underneath%20a%20US%20base%20at%20Cu%20Chi.%20Contending%20with%20organized%20guerrilla%20attacks%20on%20the%20base%2C%20the%20American%20forces%20heavily%20bombed%20the%20subterranean%20labyrinth%2C%20but%20that%20wasn't%20enough.%20The%20military%20eventually%20sent%20soldiers%20known%20as%20%26quot%3BTunnel%20Rats%26quot%3B%20down%20there.%20Lightly%20armed%20with%20a%20pistol%20and%20some%20other%20supplies%2C%20they%20faced%20threats%20like%20booby%20traps%2C%20animals%2C%20and%20enemy%20fighters.%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMore%20recently%2C%20Western%20forces%20dealt%20with%20Islamic%20State%20and%20al-Qaeda%20tunnels%20in%20places%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.army.mil%2Farticle%2F6660%2Fal_qaeda_tunnel_network_destroyed%5C%22%3EIraq%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fnews%2Fworldviews%2Fwp%2F2017%2F04%2F14%2Fthe-islamic-state-has-tunnels-everywhere-its-making-them-much-harder-to-defeat%2F%5C%22%3EAfghanistan%3C%2Fa%3E.%20In%202017%2C%20the%20US%20famously%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fworld%2Fmassive-us-bomb-in-afghanistan-killed-36-from-islamic-state-say-local-officials%2F2017%2F04%2F14%2Fdae924e4-20dd-11e7-a0a7-8b2a45e3dc84_story.html%3Fhpid%3Dhp_hp-top-table-main_afghanbomb433am%253Ahomepage%252Fstory%5C%22%3Edropped%3C%2Fa%3E%20one%20of%20the%20largest%20non-nuclear%20bombs%20it%20has%20%E2%80%94%20the%20GBU-43%20Massive%20Ordnance%20Air%20Blast%20(MOAB)%2C%20or%20Mother%20of%20all%20Bombs%20%E2%80%94%20on%20a%20collection%20of%20ISIS-K%20tunnels%20and%20bunkers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%