nd%20protecting%20plants%20from%20insects%20and%20fungus%20attacks.%20Enzymes%20act%20as%20both%20fertilisers%20and%20insecticides%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%20homemaker.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENita%20shares%20five%20easy%20tips%20on%20how%20to%20make%20bio%20enzymes%20from%20kitchen%20and%20garden%20waste%20at%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFollow%20the%203%3A1%3A10%20formula%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20main%20ingredient%20needed%20to%20make%20bio%20enzymes%20can%20be%20neem%2C%20lemon%20peels%2C%20banana%20peels%2C%20etc.%20Apart%20from%20that%20you%20would%20need%20jaggery%20and%20water.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CCut%20the%20main%20ingredients%20into%20small%20parts%2C%20then%20mix%20300%20grams%20of%20this%20with%20100%20grams%20of%20jaggery%20in%201%2C000%20ml%20of%20water.%20Mix%20the%20contents%20well.%20Irrespective%20of%20the%20main%20ingredient%2C%20one%20should%20add%20contents%20in%20their%20respective%20ratio%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENita%20adds%20that%20marigold%20enzyme%20enhances%20flowering%20growth%2C%20while%20orange%20and%20lemon%20peels%20aid%20the%20growth%20of%20plants%20like%20roses%20and%20lilies%20in%20acidic%20soil.%20Neem%20enzyme%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20serves%20as%20an%20insecticide%20or%20fungicide.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FNita-Singh-1697539544.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Nita%20makes%20bio%20enzymes%20from%20neem%20leaves%2C%20marigolds%2C%20orange%20peels%2C%20lemons%2C%20and%20bananas.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FNita-Singh-1697539544.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FNita-Singh-1697539544-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FNita-Singh-1697539544-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FNita-Singh-1697539544-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FNita-Singh-1697539544-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-332399%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ENita%20makes%20bio%20enzymes%20from%20neem%20leaves%2C%20marigolds%2C%20orange%20peels%2C%20lemons%2C%20and%20bananas.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EStore%20in%20plastic%20containers%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3ENita%20advises%20that%20the%20mixture%20should%20be%20kept%20in%20plastic%20bottles.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDo%20not%20store%20the%20contents%20in%20a%20glass%20bottle%20as%20the%20mixture%20releases%20ample%20amounts%20of%20gases.%20If%20you%20keep%20it%20in%20a%20glass%20bottle%2C%20it%20will%20explode%20and%20might%20cause%20harm.%20Even%20when%20kept%20in%20plastic%20bottles%2C%20one%20needs%20to%20loosen%20the%20cap%20in%20a%20few%20days%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShe%20notes%2C%20%E2%80%9CAlso%2C%20one%20must%20take%20a%20two-litre%20bottle%20to%20store%20one%20litre%20of%20mixture%20as%20it%20will%20allow%20some%20space%20for%20fermentation.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EKeep%20in%20the%20dark%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EAny%20fertiliser%20must%20be%20stored%20in%20a%20dark%20place%2C%20says%20Nita.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20good%20bacteria%20in%20the%20fertiliser%20will%20die%20if%20the%20containers%20are%20kept%20in%20sunlight.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20to%20spray%20the%20enzymes%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3ENita%20says%20it%20takes%20three%20months%20to%20ready%20the%20enzymes.%20It%20has%20the%20aroma%20of%20a%20vinegar.%20After%20the%20batch%20is%20ready%2C%20gardeners%20can%20mix%201